                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Oh my... something something.
<br />

<br />
Each enchanter has his own style, but I STRONGLY recommend getting mobs down evenly and then invis'ing + nuking them both down.
<br />

<br />
For starters, you don't have a 33% exp penalty and don't need to burn mana with slow/haste. 
<br />

<br />
Second, you will be , in essence, killing 2 mobs at once, for less mana, faster then you kill 2 with the haste/slow method.
<br />

<br />
If your ex-pet reaches you, there is also a smaller risk of death, since its not hasted....
<br />

<br />
Oh well, to each his own.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />'I learned long ago to cover my back and attack from behind'
<br />

<br />
               -- Cidolfas Orlandu</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
